{"tid":893700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<台電競隊遭DQ> 台灣選手：我們的護照是綠色的TAIWAN，不是紅色的CHINA","createTime":"2018-11-07T23:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T04:43:29.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7837640afc1026c1a56be80b5e38bffe2a4c1d0e","tid":893700,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:55:22.000Z","msg":"台電競隊因「國籍問題」得勝遭DQ<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞<br />\n <br />\n台灣CS電競隊Sad Story在預賽大比數擊敗日本隊。<br />\n<br />\n台灣在國際場合的「國籍歸屬」一直以來都是敏感問題，就連在電子競技賽場上也不例外。台灣CS（絕對武力）戰隊日前參加英特爾極限高手盃大賽（簡稱IEM）舉行的2019 Katowice ESEA的資格賽，台灣戰隊「Sad Story」在預賽第一場，以懸殊比數16:1完勝對手日本代表隊，但就在拿下勝利沒有多久，竟被主辦方因「國籍問題」判定喪失資格。<br />\n<br />\n被要求以中國賽區作賽<br />\n<br />\n台灣選手CrazyFace在臉書上表示，官方要他們報名「中國賽區」，但這兩年多來，他們都是以「東亞或東南亞」賽區參賽。<span style=\"color: red;\">「我們很久之前也以為是要（報名）中國（賽區）比賽，但是中國（賽區）比賽需要「中國護照」，問題是我們的護照是綠色的TAIWAN，不是紅色的CHINA。」</span>結果這次他們竟然因為整個賽區裏面找不到「台灣」，整個戰隊被淘汰，令人非常錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n事件鬧到美國最大網絡論壇「Reddit」上，更一度成為熱門話題。電子競技聯盟（ESL）代表在網上回應稱，儘管此事令人遺憾，他們也深感抱歉，但根據比賽的文件，早有列出了所有國家應該在哪個賽區。「報名時就有跟您說明，你們該報名哪個地區/國家，結果台灣沒被列入任何一區，這一點您應該向ESL官方反映。」而至於為何台灣沒有被列在「國家」裏面，他表示：「我們使用的是『聯合國列出的國家和地區』作為分類標準，我沒有興趣討論全球政治議題。」<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n台仔明明攞住個係&quot;中華民國護照&quot;<br />\n內頁國籍：republic of CHINA<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.funtop.tw/2016/10/161001-taiwan-passport/taiwan-passport_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.funtop.tw%2F2016%2F10%2F161001-taiwan-passport%2Ftaiwan-passport_3.jpg&h=206fc0b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83bb55215adae0dd1af8f484ba958b72cd460fe8","tid":893700,"uid":41308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:59:48.000Z","msg":"Republic of China不等於China"},{"pid":"f573c1dc2aca791875df4c51fac3cf4f0f3c8a6e","tid":893700,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83bb55215adae0dd1af8f484ba958b72cd460fe8","tid":893700,"uid":41308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:59:48.000Z","msg":"Republic of China不等於China"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nchina係應該參加中國區"},{"pid":"432a81fb2990c2fb9d70362eab9aee0286008a32","tid":893700,"uid":194877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:05:12.000Z","msg":"台灣都冇咩國家承認地位<br />\n話佢係中國又唔係<br />\n話佢係中華民國又冇人識"},{"pid":"153238f5b41f41c2e05f0d63652f49af3a511788","tid":893700,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"係未即係Intel唔認台灣係中國一部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b28ddbde8bea9f52366338258b4e516847dc63","tid":893700,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d1ielco78gv5pf.cloudfront.net/assets/clear-495a83e08fc8e5d7569efe6339a1228ee08292fa1f2bee8e0be6532990cb3852.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd1ielco78gv5pf.cloudfront.net%2Fassets%2Fclear-495a83e08fc8e5d7569efe6339a1228ee08292fa1f2bee8e0be6532990cb3852.gif&h=af1f18d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台仔攞住國民黨中華民國國旗<br />\n話係台灣國旗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c297025d04a4c6aced904d5c2c06c29dcafa3d7","tid":893700,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32b28ddbde8bea9f52366338258b4e516847dc63","tid":893700,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d1ielco78gv5pf.cloudfront.net/assets/clear-495a83e08fc8e5d7569efe6339a1228ee08292fa1f2bee8e0be6532990cb3852.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd1ielco78gv5pf.cloudfront.net%2Fassets%2Fclear-495a83e08fc8e5d7569efe6339a1228ee08292fa1f2bee8e0be6532990cb3852.gif&h=af1f18d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台仔攞住國民黨中華民國國旗<br />\n話係台灣國旗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\